description:
Patients with diseases of the lung or pleural tumors;
Patients with benign diseases of the lungs and pleura, as well as with lung and pleural metastases of other primary tumors;
Healthy control subjects from population-based controls from the study region (Einwohnermeldeamt)

BTLB is one of the three collections of the CRB-HSM biobank. It includes:
- FFPE and crio-preserved tissues  from tumors (mainly breast, lung, colon), whole blood, serum, plasma, nucleic acids, urine, saliva, blood cell fractions;
- DNA from lymphoprolipherative disorders;
- biopsies from abdominal aorta, carotid, safena.
